	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My music engine assumes 3606 frames per minute for NTSC and 3000 per minute for PAL. You can see all the calculations on the wiki: <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Clock_rate" class="postlink">a bunch of NES timings</a>

		

		</td>
